---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { getConfig } from '../utils/config';

const config = getConfig();
---

<Layout title="About">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 md:py-20">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
        About XXCC Unicorn Press
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 leading-relaxed italic">
        An independent publishing initiative dedicated to documenting the research and papers of Xiayu Tan and Yifei Fan.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="prose prose-lg prose-gray max-w-none mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 border-b-2 border-blue-100 pb-2">The Publisher</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>XXCC Unicorn Press</strong> is a specialized publishing house founded to provide a formal and permanent home for the academic and scientific contributions of <strong>Xiayu Tan</strong> and <strong>Yifei Fan</strong>. Our mission is to ensure that their research papers are preserved and presented with professional publication standards, providing a centralized archive for their collaborative and individual work.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4 border-b-2 border-blue-100 pb-2">The Journal</h2>
      <p>
        The <strong>Journal of XXCC Unicorn</strong> is the primary vehicle for this archive. It focuses on recording high-impact research, theoretical explorations, and innovative problem-solving across various multidisciplinary fields. Each issue of the journal is dedicated to a single, comprehensive research paper, serving as a definitive record of a specific study or discovery.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4 border-b-2 border-blue-100 pb-2">Digital Archiving</h2>
      <p>
        To ensure transparency and accessibility, every issue of the journal is archived as an independent repository within the <a href={config.publisher.githubOrg} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">XXCC Unicorn Press GitHub Organization</a>. This approach guarantees that the full context, including source data, manuscripts, and version history, remains open and verifiable for the long term.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4 border-b-2 border-blue-100 pb-2">Editorial Board & Contributors</h2>
      <p>The press is managed and maintained by:</p>
      <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-4">
        {config.editors.map((editor) => (
          <li class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="font-bold text-gray-900">{editor.name}</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-2">{editor.role}</div>
            <a href={`mailto:${editor.email}`} class="text-blue-600 text-sm hover:underline">{editor.email}</a>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4 border-b-2 border-blue-100 pb-2">Licensing & Open Access</h2>
      <p>
        XXCC Unicorn Press is committed to open dissemination of knowledge. The source code and infrastructure of this platform are licensed under the <strong>MIT License</strong>.
      </p>
      <p>
        Individual research papers and journal issues are hosted in their respective repositories and are subject to the specific licensing terms provided within those archives.
      </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="mt-20 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-800 transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
        Back to Publications
      </a>
    </footer>
  </article>
</Layout>